	<h3 class="accordion-toggle accordion-heading">How will I get to work each day?</h3>
	<div class="accordion-inner faq-border">
		<p>Because iXperience Lodging is centrally located, most of our partner companies are a 10-15 minute walk from your accommodation. For the handful that are a little further away, iX will arrange and pay for your transportation. This will be handled exclusively through Uber For Business accounts, meaning safe and convenient transport each day.</p>
	</div>

